# Espresso shot ++
- double shot espresso
- 6g nesquik
- [OPTIONAL - real chocolate] 10g (2 squares) cadbury 45% dark choc
- [OPTIONAL - chai] - 1.2g chai powder

# Milk
- 200g milk
- cubed ice
- 4g sugar
- (1 small scoop) vanilla ice cream
- [OPTIONAL - chai] - 20g honey

# Steps
1. pull shot over chocolate and nesquik
2. shake milk mix in a cocktail shaker
3. pour milk over espresso mix like a normal coffee
